parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of power steering assist can cause loss of control of the vehicle, making it difficult or impossible to steer, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: sudden loss of power steering while driving
power steering failure after stopping and restarting the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of various electronic systems can cause confusion, distraction, and loss of control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: heat and windows not functioning properly
rear windshield washer pumping out fluid continuously

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of automatic forward collision braking can cause sudden and unexpected braking, leading to accidents or injuries.

The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to come to a complete stop while driving, which can lead to accidents and put the occupants, including young children, at high risk of injury or death.
symptoms: the vehicle comes to a complete stop
the check engine light comes on
the transmission needs to be replaced multiple times.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling without warning can cause accidents, especially when driving on major city streets, and can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The engine stops running without warning
the engine can be started after several tries
the fuel pump module may need to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The reduction of engine power can cause the vehicle to hesitate or lose acceleration, which can lead to accidents, especially when driving at high speeds or merging onto busy roads.
symptoms: The vehicle displays a "Engine Power is Reduced" warning message
the vehicle hesitates or loses power when accelerating
the vehicle's engine RPMs increase to high levels (e.g.
5000RPM) while the vehicle's speed is limited (e.g.
abnormal noises coming from the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the camera system can reduce the driver's visibility, increasing the risk of accidents or damage to the vehicle, especially when parking or maneuvering in tight spaces.
symptoms: and/or front camera fail to turn on
